# Profitbricks Public REST API

Profitbricks REST API allows creation and manipulation of Virtual Datacenters and it's components.

[Official user documentation](http://devops.profitbricks.com/api/rest)

# Group Datacenter

## Datacenters collection [/datacenters]
### Retrieve datacenters [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.profitbricks.collection+json)

    + Headers

            ETag: 123whatever

    + Body
    
